args: Dimly lit stone corridors leading into the\ngreat unknown? Check aaaaand check!
Now THIS is what I'm talking about.\nThis is the adventure I dreamed of!
You look like you're having a surprising\namount of fun given where we are.
I've never seen someone so excited to\nbe in such a foreboding place. Aren't\nyou the least bit afraid to be here?
Nope! No fear. Just the thrill of...\nADVENTURE!
I feel like I've made my way into one of\nthe legends of old.
We're going to make our way to the depths\nof this ruin and find a treasure chest...
WITH the legendary knife inside!\nAaaaaaah! I am beyond chuffed!
Augh! Look! Chest! A proper treasure chest!
All right, I'm all fired up. Time to use my\nlockpicking skills to actually pick a lock!
Guess it's here to guard the chest, huh?
But if you think I'm gonna back down now,\nyou blasted fiend, you've got another thing\ncoming!
Okay! Now you guys hold that thing off\nwhile I open the chest!
Help us with the fiend, THEN open the...\nShe's totally not listening to me, is she?
...Ooooh, I see what kind of lock this is.\nEasy-peasy!
First I need to do thiiis...
Then I need to do this, and... Ah! I did it!\nIt opened, it opened, it opeeeeened!
...Oh, are you SERIOUS?!\nIt's crammed full of GEMS!
Rubbish gems! Why can't you be a\nlegendary knife?!
Um, if you're finished over there, maybe\nyou can help us out?
Ah! Sorry! Got distracted by the chest.\nI'm on my waâ€”
OH MY GOSH, THERE'S ANOTHER CHEST!
Look at the lock on THIS one.\nThis is gonna take a while...
